# Dev: `package.json` "proxy" forwards browser calls like /api/... to your backend (avoids CORS).
# Default proxy target is http://localhost:8080 — change "proxy" there if your API uses another port.
# After changing proxy, restart `npm start`.
#
# Production / direct API URL (optional; enables CORS on the API):
# REACT_APP_API_BASE=https://your-api.example.com/api
